</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Provjera CKP senzora i ploče senzora
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CMP senzor
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Prolaz ulja OCV-a
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Aktuator CMP-a
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vrijeme otvaranja ventila
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0014: Preuranjen pomak položaja ili performanse sustava bregastog vratila &#34;B&#34;
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Izmjereni CMP na ispuhu ne doseže ciljani CMP na ispuhu tijekom određenog vremena.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(logika detekcije 3 ciklusa vožnje)
</ptxt>
</entry>
